sion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 2-4 party game with your friends at custom match</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Level up as much as possible within 5 minutes to gain abilities and power up</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A total of 36 unique abilities for Guardians.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 different Bosses with completely different playstyles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 12 Boss perks to customize your playstyle further!</p></li></ul>",
